{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_10_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 すっごく頼りになる、大事な",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――インタビューと撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the interview and photo shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.0999999126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て、この衣装すっごく可愛いと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ look‚ don’t you think this outfit is super cute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0999999126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "おうちデートにぴったりの\n可愛いルームウェアを用意してくれたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They prepared cute loungewear\nthat’s perfect for a home date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.9569161177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのもいいわよね、気分上がるし……\nプライベートでも一着ほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like this kind of clothing. It lifts my mood…\nI want one for myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0333334208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.9028569937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "事前アンケートで\n『理想はおうちデートです』って言って良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad I said\n“my ideal date is a home date” in the pre-survey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666667541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.5987075567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "凄く似合ってますよ。でも遙子さんの理想のデートって\n元は違ったような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks great on you. But wasn't your ideal date originally\nsomething different…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "元々は山間の隠れ家カフェに行く予定だったもんね\n自然の中で過ごすのは、もちろん好きよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Originally‚ I planned to go to a hidden café in the mountains.\nI do like spending time in nature‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7894789138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "キャンプとか廃墟巡りも大好き\nでも、それってデートじゃなくても楽しいのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also love camping and exploring ruins.\nBut those are fun even if it’s not a date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8666667541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "私のデートの思い出は、おうちデート\nだから撮影のコンセプトも、おうちデートが良かったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of my date memories… are home dates.\nSo I’m glad the photo shoot concept is a home date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1271429458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、こないだは本当にありがとうね\n大事な思い出が出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ thank you so much for that.\nI've made a precious memory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3948074418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど\n遙子さんの役に立てたみたいで良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nI’m glad I could be of help to you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6666667541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ始まるみたい\n撮影もインタビューも、期待しててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like it’s about time to start.\nLook forward to the photo shoot and interview.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5666667541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "理想の恋人像、ですか？　……そうですね\n一緒にいると落ち着ける人です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My ideal boyfriend? …Let’s see.\nSomeone I can feel at ease with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "ドキドキワクワクも大事だけど\nほっと一息つけるっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The feeling of excitement is important‚\nbut so is being able to relax and take a breather…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にはしゃげる人もいいけど\n安心して寄りかかれる人が、私の理想です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nice to be with someone I can have fun with‚\nbut my ideal is someone I can lean on with peace of mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666667541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "だって、とっても大事にしてもらえてる、って\n実感出来るので――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it truly makes me feel\nreally cherished――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……そういえば、遙子さんの好きなタイプって）\n（初めて聞いたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Come to think of it‚ this is the first time）\n（I’ve heard about Haruko-san’s type.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8392210917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "今ほしいもの……\nおうちデート用の、可愛いルームウェアがほしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want now…\nI want some cute loungewear for a home date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9999960185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "理想のおうちデートを満喫するには\nやっぱり可愛いデート服がなくっちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To fully enjoy an ideal home date‚\nhaving cute clothes is a must.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0666626852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666600006,
          "startTime": 129.5333293518
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.0295006668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様～！\n楽しくて喋り過ぎちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work~!\nI talked too much because it was so fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0333293518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありませんよ\n遙子さんらしい、いい答えばかりでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all.\nAll of your answers were great‚ and very you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0999960185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8620204842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって自分のことを話すのって\n何回やってもドキドキするわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about myself like this…\nmakes me nervous every time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7577907479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "今回は特に、恋愛がテーマだったし……\nそういえば{user}君、この後予定ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially since the theme this time was love…\nBy the way‚ {user}-kun‚ do you have any plans after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0333293518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.8901163653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、遙子さんを送ったら、あとは帰るだけですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No Haruko-san‚ after I take you home‚ I’m going home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8901163653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.8333293518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ時間、あるのね！\nあのね、{user}君にお願いがあって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means you have time!\n{user}-kun‚ I have a favor to ask you――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.8333293518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.0232003128
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.0232003128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふ～ん\nあ、ねぇ、どっちがいいかな？",
      "translations": {
